    "bubble_choice_description": "A student is creating a chatbot for their school's website to help answer frequently asked questions. They want to implement natural language processing to help the chatbot better understand and respond to user input. As part of this process, they need to identify the parts of speech in user input to determine the user's intent and generate an appropriate response.",
